texts.content: {"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 10], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "今天分享的是骆驼祥子"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "祥子渴望拥有一辆自己的洋车"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "他一生最大的愿望简单而执着"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "然而生活总是充满无情的磨难"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 12], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "命运无常并非努力就能改变"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "善良和勤劳不一定带来好结果"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 11], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "底层人民的生活充满绝望"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 11], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "理想在现实面前不堪一击"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 10], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "人性在困境中逐渐扭曲"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 11], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "希望的火苗最终熄灭殆尽"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 9], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "挣扎越久却陷得越深"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 10], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "个人命运常被社会吞噬"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 10], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "悲剧并非偶然而是必然"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 10], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "活着有时只是一种煎熬"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"alpha": 1.0, "content": {"render_type": "solid", "solid": {"alpha": 1.0, "color": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0]}}}, "range": [0, 10], "size": 8, "bold": false, "italic": false, "underline": false, "strokes": [{"content": {"solid": {"alpha": 1, "color": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, "width": 0.06999999999999999}], "font": {"id": "7290445778273702455", "path": "C:/文轩体.ttf"}}], "text": "奋斗的意义被时间消磨"}
